"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/01\/12\/slave-beaten-set-free\/","url_meta":{"origin":10051,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Servants: A slave who is beaten is set free","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Suwayd ibn Muqarrin reported: He had a slave girl and someone slapped her, so he said to him, \u201cDid you not know that it is forbidden to strike the face? I was the seventh of my brothers during the lifetime of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessing be upon\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17529,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/09\/dhikr-virtue-daily\/","url_meta":{"origin":10051,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Great virtue of glorifying Allah daily","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever declares one hundred times a day, 'There is no God but Allah without any partner, to Him belongs sovereignty and all praise and He is powerful over everything,' he will have the reward of emancipating\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12523,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/27\/prophet-frees-slave-girl\/","url_meta":{"origin":10051,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Freedom: The Prophet frees a believing slave girl","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Mua\u2019wiyah ibn al-Hakam reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I have a servant-girl whom I slapped.\u201d That upset the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him. I said to him, \u201cShall I emancipate her?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cBring her to me.\u201d Then, she was brought and the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3964,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/01\/expiation-forget-to-pray\/","url_meta":{"origin":10051,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Expiation for forgetting to pray on time","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever forgets a prayer, let him pray it when he remembers. There is no expiation other than this.\u201d Then, the Prophet recited the verse, \"Perform prayer for My remembrance.\" (20:14) Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 597, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 684\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33003,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/30\/perfect-wudu-five-salawat\/","url_meta":{"origin":10051,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Perfect ablution, five prayers expiation of sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 30, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Uthman ibn Affan reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon